ance.\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1264, \"end\": 1269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999929459591, \"rank\": 7.053956362640801e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles is twice a world champion over the distance and had won his last 26 races prior to the semi-final defeat.\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1421, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He also lost both his heat and semi-final in the 100m before claiming a narrowphoto-finish victory in the final.\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1535, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After winning 100m gold, Lyles detailed some of the issues he has struggled with in a bid to inspire anyone reading to follow their dreams.\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1676, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1562, \"end\": 1567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9851446393509036, \"rank\": 0.015079032221569479, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He posted on X: 'I have Asthma, allergies, dyslexia, ADD,anxiety, andDepression.\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1758, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1702, \"end\": 1708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asthma\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Asthma\", \"types\": [\"Q12136\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asthma\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asthma\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But I will tell you that what you have does not define what you can become.\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1836, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Why Not You!'\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\":